summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing negotiation for and purchase of easements for sanitary sewer purposes across Lots 7 and 8, block 6, Portland and Puget Sound Railway Addition; and a transfer of jurisdiction of a portion of government Lot 4 Section 32, Township 24 North Range 4 East, W.M. and making an appropriation from the Municipal Sewerage 1971 Construction Fund therefor.
